 PATTERN COMPARISON TABLE
================================================================================
 
  +----------------+----------+----------+----------+----------+
  | Feature        | A-EnvVar | B-Yaml   | C-K8sSec | D-Vault  |
  +----------------+----------+----------+----------+----------+
  | Security       | Low      | Medium   | High     | Highest  |
  | Dynamic Refr.  | No       | No       | Yes      | Yes      |
  | Audit Trail    | None     | None     | K8s log  | Full     |
  | Secret Rotate  | Redeploy | Redeploy | Update+  | Vault    |
  |                |          |          | refresh  | lease    |
  | Complexity     | Low      | Low      | Medium   | High     |
  | Best For       | Dev      | Bare     | K8s no   | K8s +    |
  |                | simple   | metal/VM | Vault    | enterprise|
  +----------------+----------+----------+----------+----------+
 
